body:
It would appear that while all of the autoloading seems to work wonderfully, the unload is not unloading all of the dependencies.  Would you guys like to add the appropriate ```module-info mode remove``` branches for the dependencies?

Thanks!
Tony 

```

if { [ module-info mode load ] && ![ is-loaded zlib/1.2.11-apple-clang-11.0.0 ] } {
    module load zlib/1.2.11-apple-clang-11.0.0
}
if { [ module-info mode load ] && ![ is-loaded xz/5.2.5-apple-clang-11.0.0 ] } {
